plot: Cassandra and Murphy visit the botanical labs to check out the so-called herbal cure.

Murphy and Cassandra head to the laboratory in Minnesota and they find a group of people desperate to get the herbal cure against the zombie virus Batch 47. However the greenhouse with Batch 47 is under siege of a hybrid type of zombies entwined with plant. The researcher of Batch 47 is Odegard, who is using zombie heads in his experiment. When the survivors arrive in the spot, they decide to collect the seeds to help a girl that is sick. Murphy stumbles with Dr. Kurian and stays with him. Meanwhile the drug lord Escorpion arrives with his gang and subdue the survivors. Then he uses a great dose of Batch 47 in Odegard, killing him. What will happen to the possible herb cure?—Claudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
